Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 03/07/2025

Thank you for using our Budget Tracking App (“we”, “our”, or “PikiMoney”). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information. By using the App, you agree to the practices described in this Policy.

1. Overview
This App is a tool designed to help users track their personal expenses and view financial summaries. It is not a financial advisory service, and does not provide financial, investment, legal, or tax advice. Users are solely responsible for how they use the information generated within the App.

2. Information We Collect
a. Personal Information
We do not require users to provide personally identifiable information unless explicitly requested for a specific feature (e.g., feedback, support).

b. Device & Usage Data
We may automatically collect certain data such as:

Device type and operating system

Country or region

App usage statistics

Crash reports

c. Camera Access
The app may request access to the camera (e.g., for scanning receipts). This access is optional and used solely for user-initiated functionality. No images or data are transmitted without your interaction.

3. Third-Party Services
a. OpenAI
We use OpenAI’s API for chatbot functionality to assist users with understanding their spending. Conversations may be transmitted to OpenAI’s servers and processed in accordance with their privacy policy.

OpenAI Privacy Policy: https://openai.com/privacy

We do not use AI to make financial recommendations.

b. Google AdMob (Advertising)
We use Google AdMob to display advertisements. AdMob may collect and use your data to show personalized ads, depending on your region and choices.

Google Privacy Policy: https://policies.google.com/privacy

You may opt-out of personalized ads via your device settings.

4. Data Security
We use commercially reasonable safeguards to protect the information you provide. However, no system can be 100% secure. Use of the App is at your own risk.

5. User Responsibility & Disclaimer
This App is a self-help tool for tracking expenses.

We do not offer financial advice.

Any conclusions drawn or decisions made based on the App’s data are your own responsibility.

We are not liable for any financial losses, damages, or decisions made based on the use of this App.

6. Children’s Privacy
This App is not intended for children under 18 (or the equivalent minimum age in your jurisdiction). We do not knowingly collect data from children.

7. Privacy Policy Updates
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. You will be notified of any material changes via the app or the Play Store listing.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at:

Email: reception@1visitor.com
Developer Name: Bratovich

By using the App, you acknowledge and agree to this Privacy Policy.

